<h1 style="margin-bottom: 5px; color: #ffcc0d; font-size: 15px;">Without A Rating Widget<br />Your App Is Losing Downloads</h1>
<p>That image on the right is what the new iOS 6 App Store looks like on the iPhone.</p>
<ol>
<li>Search results show only 1 App per screen.</li>
<li>With over 870,000 Apps in the App store your App needs to be first.</li>
<li>Keywords and search terms are only <em>part</em> of the solution.</li>
<li>Ratings &amp; Reviews are the rest.</li>
<li>A steady stream of good Ratings &amp; Reviews move Apps to the front.</li>
</ol>
<p>Our rating widget works by using App Analytics to ask only the best users to rate your App.</p>
<p>Best of all, AskingPoint App Analytics with the Ratings Booster is <span style="text-decoration: underline;">free</span>.</p>
